{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A short indie horror game where you explore the mysterious Kukuriku Island, uncover traces of an ancient civilization, and navigate the shadowy forces at play.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CHOREOGRAPHED EVENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212260/extras/stoned-choreographed-events.gif?t=1736591154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a world where the story unfolds around you in real-time through scripted events. No cutscenes, no interruptions\u2014just you in control. Dive into conversations, eavesdrop, or walk away\u2014it's your call.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PHYSICAL INTERACTIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212260/extras/stoned-phisical-interactions.gif?t=1736591154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with the world naturally, pulling, pushing, and grabbing. Every action feels tactile, opening the door to immersive and quirky gameplay moments.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">IMMERSIVE ENVIRONMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212260/extras/stoned-ambience.gif?t=1736591154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lose yourself in a meticulously crafted environment. PSX-ish style visuals, rich soundscapes and sound effects bring every moment to life.\u00a0Hear sounds change as you move, get muffled behind walls, or echo in certain spaces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Contextual dialogues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Realtime choreographed cutscenes and events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Physical interactions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immersive volumetric audio</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wishlist now to get updates and be the first to experience the haunting mystery when it releases!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212260/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736591154","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212260/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736591154","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212260/3208da077f8c7715732822468eb2a5a8e9d40a72/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736591154","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212260/3208da077f8c7715732822468eb2a5a8e9d40a72/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736591154","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A short indie horror game where you explore the mysterious Kukuriku Island, uncover traces of an ancient civilization, and navigate the shadowy forces at play.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CHOREOGRAPHED EVENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212260/extras/stoned-choreographed-events.gif?t=1736591154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a world where the story unfolds around you in real-time through scripted events. No cutscenes, no interruptions\u2014just you in control. Dive into conversations, eavesdrop, or walk away\u2014it's your call.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PHYSICAL INTERACTIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212260/extras/stoned-phisical-interactions.gif?t=1736591154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with the world naturally, pulling, pushing, and grabbing. Every action feels tactile, opening the door to immersive and quirky gameplay moments.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">IMMERSIVE ENV